1. *Vidiš* kako sunce lepo sija danas. (You see how the sun is shining beautifully today.)
2. Ne mogu da *vidim* ništa bez naočara. (I can't see anything without my glasses.)
3. *Vidi* ovu sliku, baš je lepa. (Look at this picture, it's really nice.)
4. Oni *vide* da je to pogrešno, ali ništa ne rade. (They see that it's wrong, but they're not doing anything.)
5. Da li *vidiš* ove ogromne oblakere u daljini? (Do you see those huge clouds in the distance?)
6. *Videla* sam ga juče u gradu. (I saw him yesterday in town.)
7. Čim *vidim* taj film, javiću ti utiske. (As soon as I see that movie, I'll let you know my thoughts.)
8. *Vidiš li* kako je ovaj dečko simpatičan? (Do you see how this boy is cute?)
9. Ne mogu da *vidim* nijedan razlog da ostanem ovde. (I can't see any reason to stay here.)
10. Kada *vidite* nju, recite joj da me pozove. (When you see her, tell her to call me.)